channel.title: (PI) 317 Need help with Server/Teleport. 4 Questions
channel.description:
Please need help with any one of these questions, if yu know one of them please comment below.
1.Recently I changed the ::tele coordinates on the magic tab (Home-Varrock, etc.). When I compiled it, I logged back into the client to check and the hole magic emblems where gone so now there is nothng in the like the inventory(backpack tab). What do I need to do to make it come back because theres nothing in there?
2. When I compile stuff I usely get this message but usely can compile basic thing like Client title, ingame messages, edit log in. This message from compile all the time:
Note: Some input files use unchecked or unsafe operations. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:unchecke for detais. Pressy any keyto continue . . .
Is ths normal? or do I need to edit something in one of my .java files?
3. I need some help changing PvP World to a Eco World.
4. When I click around the game and press tabs, The client freeze makingme have to start it all back up, does anyoe have any info on this problem?

[quote=“C2dahizzy, post:4, topic:478140”][quote author=kickingjamie link=topic=596338.msg4199076#msg4199076 date=1357914652]
@4 - Something to do with your server trying to load interfaces that your client doesn’t support/have. Are you using the same client that came with your server?
[/quote]

Yes, I was useing a completely different client[/quote][quote=“Si Force, post:2, topic:478140”]@1 - Can you show us all the changes you made? Also did you make any other changes whatsoever?
@2 - That’s normal and means that your client compiled successfully.
@3 - I won’t go on teamviewer or anything like that, so can you please post your problem here so I can help you here?
@4 - It sounds like you run a terrible source to be honest, I can’t help you with that one.[/quote]

@1 - Ok I see what the problemwas it was because it was a alter of guthix, when I press it my magic emblems disappear.
@3 -I don’t mind, lets teamview… Cause I have no clue on how to remove PvP from source to eco world.
[/quote]
That isnt really hard, remove the spawn commands and master commands then change shop prices in prices.txt now u must go into player.java and comment out al the wildy and safespot coords u dont want
